{"word":"H5999 - עָמָל - ʻâmâl - aw-mawl' - Grievance","slug":"H5999","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָמָל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻâmâl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-mawl'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Grievance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05DE;&#x05DC; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;ma&#x0302;l</b> - <i>aw-mawl'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5998\">H5998</a>; <i>toil</i>, that is, <i>wearing effort</i>; hence <i>worry</i>, whether of body or mind: - grievance (-vousness), iniquity, labour, mischief, miserable (-sery), pain (-ful), perverseness, sorrow, toil, travail, trouble, wearisome, wickedness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5998\">H5998</a>, <a href=\"#/H6000\">H6000</a>, <a href=\"#/H6001\">H6001</a>, <a href=\"#/H6002\">H6002</a>, <a href=\"#/H6003\">H6003</a>"}]}